  m_text: 'the scale image represents the damage dealt to you and to the opponant.
    if the number is in in yellow that means its in your favor . if its blue that
    means that you are lossing. And the first person to make the scale hit 20 in
    his favor wins the match. And Remmember the right side of the scale is you and
    the lrft is the opponant.

